{
  "chapter": "050",
  "title": "楚元王世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚元王刘交</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的同母小弟，字<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘交\">游（刘交）</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，已经在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>地[禽|擒获了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚王韩信</span>，于是封弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘交\">交（刘交）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>，建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘郢\">郢（刘郢）</span>继位。"
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王戊</span>继位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">冬</span>季，因为在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>服丧期间私通淫乱获罪，被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">削</span>去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海郡</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">春</span>季，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戊</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王</span>合谋<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>叛，他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张尚</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太傅</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵夷吾</span>劝谏，不听。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戊</span>就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张尚\">尚（张尚）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵夷吾\">夷吾（赵夷吾）</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">起兵</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>一起向西<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘壁</span>。到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>以南，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周亚夫</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军截断<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粮</span>道，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>饥饿，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">走</span>逃，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚王戊</span>自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">军</span>队于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>已经<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平</span>定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之乱，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span>打算以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">德侯</span>的儿子继承<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>的祀，以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚元王\">元王（楚元王）</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘礼\">礼（刘礼）</span>继承<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的祀。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王</span>，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">老人</span>家，应当为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗室</span>率先行善。如今却首先<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">率</span>领<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">七国</span>作乱，扰乱天下，怎么还能延续他的后嗣！\"不允许继承<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>的祀，准许立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的后嗣。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘礼\">礼（刘礼）</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宗正</span>。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘礼\">礼（刘礼）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>，奉祀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚元王\">元王（楚元王）</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚文王</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚文王\">文王（楚文王）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚安王\">安王（楚安王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘道\">道（刘道）</span>继位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚安王\">安王（楚安王）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十二年（时长）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚襄王\">襄王（楚襄王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘注\">注（刘注）</span>继位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚襄王\">襄王（楚襄王）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十四年（时长）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘纯\">纯（刘纯）</span>继位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘纯\">纯（刘纯）</span>继位后，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">地节二年</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">中人</span>上书告发<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚王纯\">楚王（楚王纯）</span>谋<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚王纯\">王（楚王纯）</span>自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>，并入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>成为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城郡</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    "5.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵王刘遂</span>，他的父亲是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">中子</span>，名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘友\">友（刘友）</span>，谥号为\"幽\"。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵幽王\">幽王（赵幽王）</span>因忧虑而死，所以谥为\"幽\"。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕禄</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>去世。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>诛<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛</span>杀诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕禄</span>等人，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵幽王\">幽王（赵幽王）</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘遂\">遂（刘遂）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>即位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘遂\">遂（刘遂）</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘辟彊\">辟彊（刘辟彊）</span>，取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河间郡</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">河间王</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：河间文王\">文王（河间文王）</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十三年（时长）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘福\">福（刘福）</span>继位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>去世，无子，绝后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>，并入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    "7.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘遂\">遂（刘遂）</span>已经做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span>时因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晁错</span>检举的过错被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">削</span>去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵王遂\">赵王（赵王遂）</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>郡。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>叛，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵王遂</span>与他们合谋<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">起兵</span>。他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">建德</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王悍</span>劝谏，不听。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘遂\">遂（刘遂）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">烧杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">建德</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王悍</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发兵</span>屯驻在西部边界，想等候<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军一同西进。向北派使者到<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，与之联合<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">曲周侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦寄</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵王遂</span>退回，据守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>城，相持<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七月（时长）</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>北，不能西进。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>听说这个消息，也停止行动，不肯侵入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>边境。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾布</span>自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>归来，于是合兵引<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">水</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灌</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>城。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>城崩坏，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵王遂\">赵王（赵王遂）</span>自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵幽王</span>绝后。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    "8.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：国家将要兴起，必有祥瑞征兆，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君子</span>被任用而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">小人</span>退避。国家将要灭亡，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤人</span>隐退，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">乱臣</span>显贵。假使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚王戊</span>不施<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刑</span>于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申公</span>，遵从他的言论，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">防</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先生</span>，哪里会有<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">篡</span>位<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>戮的阴谋，成为天下的<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">僇</span>笑柄呢？<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤人</span>啊，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤人</span>啊！不是本质上具有其内涵，怎么能任用他们呢？真是深刻啊，\"安危在于发号施令，存亡在于所任用的人\"，这话说得真对啊！"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>分封<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">同姓</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>有美名。 已经<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>称王。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穆生</span>摆设<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">醴</span>酒，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韦孟</span>作诗规劝。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王戊</span>抛弃<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>行，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>连兵反叛。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">太后（窦太后）</span>任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘礼\">礼（刘礼）</span>，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国处罚从轻。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚文王\">文（楚文王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚襄王\">襄（楚襄王）</span>相继即位，世代涌现才俊。 无奈<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘遂\">赵遂（刘遂）</span>，接连败坏其声名！ 兴亡的征兆，所任用之人应该明察。"
    }
  }
}